I '''Robert Abbott''' (mibait 1933) metung yang  [[United States|American]]ung pialung a talaimbentu.

I Abbott metung yang maranun a computer programmer, magobra keng [[IBM 360]] [[assembly language]].  Maburi ya kareng t-shirt atin gulis-gulis a sasabian na atin lang kaayusan. Iya ing megdesing keng  [[chess]] variant [[Baroque chess]] (bantug mu naman bilang Ultima); ing pialung a baraha [[Eleusis (game)|Eleusis]]; ampo ing [[Crossings (game)|Crossings]] ampo [[Epaminondas (game)|Epaminondas]]. Dakal kareng kayang pialung atiu la keng kayang aklat a, ''Abbott's New Card Games'' (Stein & Day 1963). 

Kapilan pamu minalis ing kayang pamiisip keng pamanimbentu kareng ausan dang "[[Logic Maze]]s" o "Mazes a atin tuntunan".  Ding kayang bantug a logic mazes ilapin deng [[Theseus and the Minotaur]] makatakdang mazes, ampo ing Sliding Door Maze, nung nu mayakit la keng kayang website (lawen la reng suglung lalam).

